name: Linda's Realty
body:
**欢迎访问我的网页！**
 我是美国华盛顿州专业地产经纪人，如果你在华州有地产方面的需求，我非常乐意帮助您.
   电邮：flcheng08@gmail.com    
   电话： 425-999-6778   
   微信: chengfl_seattle    
   微博: Seattle_Realty   

我的目标就是分析周边地产的市场数据，根据成交价和挂牌价的比率，社区近期价格涨幅，为您提供专业的， 快速的专业地产信息。作为一个称职的地产经纪，我会在购房关键环节上，为你提供帮助，如以专业眼光发现房屋存在的问题，解释各种房屋有关的专业文档的检查，产权文档， 产权保险，推荐验房， 计算房贷，交接的费用等等。我会在出价和谈判过程中，充分运用专业知识和谈判技巧在保障双赢前提下最大限度地保护买方的利益。



**Welcome to my homepage**


I look forward to assisting you with your real estate needs. Feel free to email flcheng08@gmail.com, or call me at 425-999-6778.

If there is a specific property you have a question about, please send me the address or MLS# of the home and I will schedule an appointment for you.

My goal is to empower my client’s decision making process with data-driven information and provide perspective from the data analysis of the market. To work efficiently towards a pleasurable experience for you and your friends. To be a valuable resource for my clients and their continued referrals.

Do you need to find out the great deals in greater Seattle area? Write a email to me flcheng08@gmail.com and the information will send you for free!
